channel.title: Joeocity Project
channel.description:
For everyone that cant just finish making a private server, this is the project for you. I am looking for a group of 20 people to design the ultimate private server. There will only be 20 positions so contact me A.S.A.P for a position. You will have to meet a minimum of 3 requirments. The requirments are listed below. I will post my contact inforrmation below. Im not a private server expert so this is why im getting together a group. In a week or 2 joeocity.com will have all the project information on it. Please register on joeocity.com when its online. I will be making post everyday. If there is need for more information please dont hesitate to contact me.
Requirments:
-Must know Mysql -Must know php -Must be familiar with java -Must know C++ -Must have knowledge about moparscape -Must be able to code the moparscape application -Must have leadership skills
Contact Me
Email: joe@joeocity.com Aim screename: joeocity gchat name: joeocity@gmail.com
